fetchPrice(address).details: You can obtain these values by calling `TroveManager.fetchPrice()` rather than directly interacting with this contract.

params._token: Token to fetch the price for

returns._0: The latest valid price for the requested token

params._pyth: Address of the pyth oracle for this LST
